--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SUMMARY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This the README file for the NEXTENS source distribution for Linux and
Cygwin. NEXTENS stands for 'Nederlandse Extensie voor
Tekst-naar-Spraak' (Dutch extension for text-to-speech). It is an
extension to the Festival speech synthesis system providing text to
speech conversion for Dutch. For more information, see
http://nextens.uvt.nl.

 
